      "content": "Subject: Potential Next Step – Senior Developer Position\n\nDear [Candidate's Name],\n\nWe wanted to personally reach out and thank you for your incredible dedication and enthusiasm throughout the selection process for the Senior Developer position here at [Company Name]. Your technical acumen truly shone through, particularly during the final interviews, and it has been a privilege to observe your skills in action.\n\nIt breaks my heart to convey that our decision made this incredibly difficult, as ultimately we moved forward with another candidate. Please know your talent and drive are commendable, and such a complete match for our team simply wasn't [Company Name]'s top choice this time.\n\nYour passion for technology and innovation is inspiring, and we were impressed not only with your professional skills but also with your genuine approach to problem-solving. We would be more than happy to keep you in our esteemed network and wish you continued success both personally and professionally.\n\nWe genuinely hope that where we eventually cannot match your expertise to our needs at the moment, there is a way it may for the future.\n\nWarmest regards and sincere appreciation,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]\n[Contact Information]",
