      "content": "thanks for that, it's definitely warmer. one thing though—the phrasiing \"it breaks my heart\" and \"didn't match our top choice\" feels a little too heavy and maybe a bit awkward for a corporate setting. could you try one more version that's empathetic and acknowledges their strength but keeps it a bit more grounded and professional? maybe mention that it was a very close decision.",
