      "content": "Subject: Appreciation and Next Steps – Senior Developer Role\n\nDear [Candidate's Name],\n\nI am reaching out with heartfelt gratitude for your dedication and the high-caliber technical proficiency you displayed throughout the selection process for our Senior Developer role at [Company Name]. It was indeed a joy to assess your profound expertise and also to witness your impressive problem-solving skills firsthand.\n\nThe decision did not come easily. We had a very closely contested process against incredibly promising candidates, which ultimately led us in a different direction. While the outcome was not what we had hoped for, your exceptional abilities and the positive energy you bring are recognized and highly regarded by our team.\n\nOur company constantly values the nurturing of tech talents, and we'd like to assure you that we see a vast potential for you within our professional landscape. So, while we move forward, I want to maintain our line of communication and I encourage you to reach out for potential opportunities of mutual benefit.\n\nThank you for considering [Company Name] as a prospective employer, and please know that we hold you in the highest regard.\n\nSincerely,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]\n[Contact Information]",
